---
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 cv-auto">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center animate-on-scroll">
    <!-- Animated gradient border wrapper -->
    <div class="relative p-[1px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cta-border-glow">
    <div class="relative glass rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-14 overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-accent/10 transition-all duration-500">
      <!-- Animated decorative glows -->
      <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-48 h-48 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 4s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-48 h-48 bg-mauve/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 6s; animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>

      <div class="relative">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-4 tracking-tight">加入台灣社群</h2>
        <p class="text-subtext-0 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          與其他台灣的 OpenClaw 使用者交流心得、分享設定、回報問題，一起打造更好的 AI 助理體驗。
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw" variant="primary" size="lg">
            GitHub 討論區
          </Button>
          <Button href="/docs/start/getting-started" variant="secondary" size="lg">
            開始使用
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
